   "properties": {},
   "title": "README \u2014 Wan 2.2 I2V",
   "color": "#432",
   "bgcolor": "#653",
   "widgets_values": [
    "WAN 2.2 IMAGE-TO-VIDEO (Remix v3)\n\n1. Load your START IMAGE in the Load Image node \u2014 the video begins from it.\n2. Write what should HAPPEN in the positive prompt (motion, camera, mood).\n3. Defaults: 1280x720, 81 frames @16fps, interpolated to 32fps (~5s).\n\nSPEED: the two purple LoRA nodes are the Lightning 4-step LoRAs, OFF by default. Right-click each > Bypass to toggle ON, then set BOTH samplers: steps 8, cfg 1.0 (high: start 0 end 4 / low: start 4 end 8). Quality drops a little, render time drops ~5x.\n\nIf you run out of VRAM: lower resolution to 960x544, or use the GGUF loader variant installed by the 12GB profile."
   ]
  },
